data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream oasis in the heart of Winter Park, Florida. Nestled in the Seminole County neighborhood of Wrenwood Heights, this pool home offers an enchanting retreat where timeless elegance meets modern comforts. With its idyllic location and an array of exceptional features (including 10' deep pool), this residence is a rare gem that is sure to captivate your heart.    Step inside and be greeted by an interior that exudes warmth and grace. Meticulously cared for, this Winter Park charmer has already undergone thoughtful updates since the current owners purchased it, including new floors and updated bathrooms and kitchen. The natural light that floods the family room creates an inviting atmosphere, beckoning you to unwind and revel in its beauty.     For the culinary enthusiasts, the kitchen awaits your personal touch. While the current owners have added many updates since their purchase, they believe that new homeowners deserve the opportunity to select their own appliances. As a generous gesture, the sellers are offering a remarkable $5,000 buyer credit, allowing you to effortlessly customize your dream kitchen to your heart's desire.    Outside, the exterior of this home is a testament to pride of ownership. With an impeccably manicured lawn and stunning mature landscaping, the curb appeal is simply breathtaking. The roof, a vital component of any home, has been lovingly maintained and is only 11 years old, providing you with peace of mind.    Steeped in history, this half-century-old home has stood the test of time and has been a witness to countless cherished memories. The split floor plan offers versatility and can accommodate dual living arrangements or provide a haven of privacy for you and your loved ones. Embrace the opportunity to create your own chapter within these walls and start making memories that will last a lifetime.    Located in the esteemed neighborhood of Wrenwood Heights, you'll find yourself surrounded by a mature oak trees, inviting sidewalks and close proximity to just about everything expected of Winter Park living. Explore the nearby parks, indulge in the exquisite local dining options, or simply take a leisurely stroll through the tree-lined streets, immersing yourself in the beauty that East Winter Park has to offer.    Don't miss out on the chance to make this Winter Park haven your very own. With its exceptional built in features, incredible buyer credit, and prime location, this property is a rare find. Contact us today to schedule a private tour.    recent updates include: Exterior Front Refinished, Professionally Landscaped, Additional Trees Added, New Pool Pump, Pool Resurfaced & Retiled, New Vinyl Fencing, New Luxury Vinyl Flooring throughout and more..No HOA...Close before End of Year!
